This uploads commits from your local to GitHub.

âœ… Workflow 2: Pull Changes Made on GitHub (Remote â†’ Local)
ğŸ”¹ Step 1: Someone updated files on GitHub (e.g., README.md)
You want to bring those changes into your local machine.

bash
Copy
Edit
